org.letras.psi.iregion
Class RegionData

java.lang.Object
  org.letras.psi.iregion.RegionData
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRegion
public class RegionData
extends java.lang.Object
implements IRegion

The RegionData class represents Data Transfer Objects for Regions. This is useful when transfering a set of regions and can greatly reduce the reduce the number of necessary remote method calls. This class is used in the IRegionSet-Interfaces.

Author:
niklas
